<section class="section" id="promoter-profile"><div class="grid2"><div class="card"><div class="cardHead"><div class="cardTitle"><h3><i class="fa-solid fa-user-gear"></i> Profile</h3><p>Promoter identity, payout account, referral code, and verification state.</p></div><span class="badge ok"><%= dashboardData?.profile?.verificationStatus || 'active' %></span></div><form class="formPanel" method="POST" action="/promoter/profile"><input type="hidden" name="_csrf" value="<%= csrfToken || '' %>"><div class="formGrid"><div class="field"><label>Name</label><div class="control"><i class="fa-solid fa-user"></i><input name="fullName" value="<%= dashboardData?.profile?.name || dashboardShell?.profileName || '' %>"></div></div><div class="field"><label>Email</label><div class="control"><i class="fa-solid fa-envelope"></i><input name="email" type="email" value="<%= dashboardData?.profile?.email || '' %>"></div></div><div class="field"><label>Phone</label><div class="control"><i class="fa-solid fa-phone"></i><input name="phone" value="<%= dashboardData?.profile?.phone || '' %>"></div></div><div class="field full"><label>Payout account</label><div class="control"><input name="payoutAccount" value="<%= dashboardData?.profile?.payoutAccount?.account || '' %>"></div></div></div><button class="btn btnPrimary" type="submit"><i class="fa-solid fa-floppy-disk"></i> Save profile</button></form></div><div class="card"><div class="cardHead"><div class="cardTitle"><h3>Referral identity</h3><p>Primary referral code and public tracking URL.</p></div></div><div class="splitGrid"><div class="splitItem"><div class="splitTop"><span>Code</span><strong><%= dashboardData?.profile?.mainReferralCode || '-' %></strong></div></div><div class="splitItem"><div class="splitTop"><span>Status</span><span class="badge ok"><%= dashboardData?.profile?.verificationStatus || 'active' %></span></div></div><div class="splitItem" style="grid-column:1/-1"><div class="splitTop"><span>URL</span><strong><%= dashboardData?.profile?.mainReferralUrl || '-' %></strong></div></div></div></div></div><div class="card" id="verification" style="margin-top:14px"><div class="cardHead"><div class="cardTitle"><h3><i class="fa-solid fa-id-card-clip"></i> Promoter verification</h3><p>Verification is required before withdrawals and offline sales. Normal referral links remain available while review is pending.</p></div><span class="badge <%= dashboardData?.profile?.verificationStatus === 'verified' ? 'ok' : 'warn' %>"><%= dashboardData?.profile?.verificationStatus || 'pending' %></span></div><% if (currentUser?.phone && !currentUser?.phoneVerifiedAt) { %><div class="notice">Verify your phone number before promoter approval. <a href="/account/phone-verification">Verify phone</a></div><% } %><form class="formPanel" method="POST" action="/promoter/verification"><input type="hidden" name="_csrf" value="<%= csrfToken || '' %>"><div class="formGrid"><div class="field"><label>Identity document type</label><div class="control"><i class="fa-regular fa-id-card"></i><select name="documentType" required><option value="national_id">National ID</option><option value="passport">Passport</option><option value="driver_license">Driver license</option></select></div></div><div class="field"><label>Document reference</label><div class="control"><i class="fa-solid fa-hashtag"></i><input name="documentReference" required></div></div><div class="field"><label>Payout method</label><div class="control"><i class="fa-solid fa-wallet"></i><select name="payoutMethod" required><option value="Mobile Money">Mobile Money</option><option value="Bank Transfer">Bank transfer</option></select></div></div><div class="field"><label>Payout provider</label><div class="control"><i class="fa-solid fa-building-columns"></i><input name="payoutProvider" placeholder="MTN, Airtel, bank name" required></div></div><div class="field full"><label>Payout account</label><div class="control"><i class="fa-solid fa-hashtag"></i><input name="payoutAccount" value="<%= dashboardData?.profile?.payoutAccount?.account || '' %>" required></div></div><div class="field full"><label>Verification note</label><div class="control"><textarea name="notes" placeholder="Any detail needed by the verification team"></textarea></div></div><div class="field full"><label class="checkLine"><input type="checkbox" name="termsAccepted" required> I accept promoter attribution, commission, payout, privacy, and anti-fraud rules.</label></div><div class="field full"><label class="checkLine"><input type="checkbox" name="trainingAcknowledged" required> I completed the fraud and offline-sales rules acknowledgement.</label></div></div><button class="btn btnPrimary" type="submit"><i class="fa-solid fa-paper-plane"></i> Submit promoter verification</button></form></div></section>
